.cs 3 on
.cs 2 on
.cm 'Page Mode Reference' 'Updated on 05/05/83 by JDN'
MOVING THE CURSOR                        EDITING FUNCTIONS
.*<------------->                        <--------------->
.* field bold command help page cursor
.* field bold command help page functions
   CTRL-U/D/L/R = Cursor up/down/left/right   ESC I = Insert mode (toggle)
.* <---------->                               <--->
.* field command help page udlr
.* field command help page ins
   CTRL-P/N = Previous/next word              ESC S = Split current line
.* <------>                                   <--->
.* field
.* field
   CTRL-T/B = Go to top/bottom text line      ESC J = Join cur line with next
.* <------>                                   <--->
.* field
.* field
   CTRL-F/E = Go to first/end of line         ESC SPACE = Collect new lines
.* <------>                                   <------->
.* field
.* field
MOVING THROUGH THE FILE
.*<------------------->
.* field bold command help page scroll
   ESC U/D  = Move screen text up/down        ESC A = Align rest of paragraph
.* <----->                                    <--->
.* field
.* field
   ESC P/N  = Go to previous/next page        ESC Z = Justify rest of paragraph
.* <----->                                    <--->
.* field
.* field
   ESC T/B  = Put cur line at the top/bottom
.* <----->
.* field
.* field
   ESC F/E  = Go to first/end of file       DELETE C/W/L = Delete char/word/lin
.* <----->                                  <---------->
.* field
.* field
.cs 2 off
.cs 3 off
